cted to collectively be near-critical, and this\nnon-local property of gene regulatory network dynamics cannot be predicted\nusing the density of interactions alone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 17:47:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-03"}
