ficantly extend the range of\nOhnesorge number over which filament breakup has been considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 22:07:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Aug 2018 01:56:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-03"}
