nic junctions with Au\nbase electrodes and multilayer graphene base electrodes show similar electronic\nresponses. We explain this observation by the strong orbital coupling occurring\nat the bottom electrode-bis(thienyl) benzene molecules interface and by the\npinning of the hybridized molecular orbitals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 May 2018 10:54:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-07"}
